1.0.0.name: wordpress/woo-tumblog
1.0.0.description: Create a tumblr style blog using this plugin. Simply install the plugin, add the easy to use tags to your theme, and your blog will be transformed into a Tumblr-style blog. Create posts direct from the WordPress dashboard, your iPhone, or the familiar WordPress interface.
